description.narrative: 3.3. Guidance, tools and resources to effectively generate, analyze, and utilize statistical and qualitative information for Child Rights Monitoring system are available in the country., which contributes to Children In Urban Settings / Local Governance, Cross-Sectoral Monitoring, Data And Situation Analyses, Cross-Sectoral Monitoring, Data And Situation Analyses (Covid), Evaluation And Research. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: The Government of Albania - UNICEF Programme of Cooperation is effectively designed, coordinated, managed and supported to meet quality standards in achieving results for children.
